    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Anomura associated with cnidarians and poriferans collected from Northwestern Bay of Bengal: A, Allogalathea elegans (Adams & White, 1848); B, Petrolisthes lamarckii (Leach, 1820); C, Porcellanella triloba White, 1851; D, Polyonyx hendersoni Southwell, 1909; E, Pisidia gordoni (Johnson, 1970)." ;
